### Salud pública
GET http://localhost:8080/public/health

### Listar reglas (requiere JWT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Obtener regla por id (requiere JWT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rules/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Crear regla (requiere rol ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Regla A",
  "description": "Descripción",
  "isActive": true
}

### Actualizar regla (requiere rol ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/rules/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Regla A2",
  "description": "Nueva descripción",
  "isActive": true
}

### Toggle activo/inactivo (requiere rol ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rules/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}

### Eliminar regla (requiere rol ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/rules/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt}}
